And what if this person were given information by this space-being that explained the secret history of life on Earth and its pending future? 		<div class="gal-wrapper">
			<div id="gal-scroller">
				<div class="slider" id="gal-scroller-slider" style="width: 582px;">
					<div class="slider-content">
	<div id="gal-slide-0" class="slide" style="width: 582px;">
<div class="gal-item">
<div class="image"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2"><img src="./Intelligent Design for Atheists - The Raelian Movement_files/intelligent_icon.png" style="width:120px;height:180px" alt=""></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2">Intelligent Design - Message from the Designers</a></div><div class="text">Years ago, everybody knew that the earth was flat, everybody knew that the sun revolved around the earth, and today everybody knows that life on earth is either the result of random evolution or the work of a supernatural God.<br>Or is it? In “Message from the Designers”, Rael presents us with the vast amount of information that he received during his UFO encounters in 1973 - a third option: all life on earth having been created by advanced scientists from another world.<br></div></div></div><div id="gal-slide-1" class="slide" style="width: 582px;">
<div class="gal-item">
<div class="image"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2"><img src="./Intelligent Design for Atheists - The Raelian Movement_files/cloning_icon.jpg" style="width:120px;height:180px" alt=""></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2">Yes to human cloning</a></div><div class="text">Today’s new cloning technology is the first step in the quest for immortality or eternal life.
What past religions used to promise only after death in a mythical paradise will soon be a scientific reality here on Earth – this is Rael’s challenging conclusion in an incisive and wide-ranging review of how science is about to revolutionize all our lives.<br>With rare vision, Rael sketches details of an amazing future in which our nascent technology will revolutionize and transform the world.<br></div></div></div><div id="gal-slide-2" class="slide" style="width: 582px;">
<div class="gal-item">

<div class="title"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2">The Maitreya: Extracts from his Teachings</a></div><div class="text">Rael, the predicted “Maitreya from the West”, shares his teachings and insights in this wonderful book of extracts taken from the many Raelian seminars at which he has taught over the past 30 years.
A multitude of topics are covered in this book, including love, happiness, serenity, spirituality, contemplation, the myth of perfection, non-violence, science, loving relationships and much more.<br>This is essential reading for anyone interested in developing his or her potential and wishing to live a more fulfilling and joyful life..<br></div></div></div><div id="gal-slide-3" class="slide" style="width: 582px;">

<div class="title"><a href="http://www.rael.org/download.php?list.2">Geniocracy: Government of the people, for the people, by the Geniuses</a></div><div class="text">“Geniocracy,” the 1st English edition of Rael's classic work, allows a new generation to consider an ingenious worldwide solution to man’s biggest problems: war, hunger, poverty and the exploitation of genius under “mediocracies” backed by military might.<br>The solution, says the author, is geniocracy: collegial government by geniuses elected under a selective democracy.<br></div></div></div><div id="gal-slide-5" class="slide" style="width: 582px;">

<title>HAPPY SCIENCE Official Website</title>

<meta name="description" content="Official Website of HAPPY SCIENCE. HAPPY SCIENCE is a worldwide religious organization that spreads spiritual teachings to solve problems in life with love, enlightenment and faith. Our main teachings is the Fourfold Path which are “Love,” “Wisdom,” “Self-Reflection” and “Progress,” also called “The Principle of Happiness.” Members of HAPPY SCIENCE have faith in Lord El Cantare, the supreme God whose mission is to bring happiness to all humanity. The HAPPY SCIENCE GROUP is actively involved in many fields in addition to religion such as education, politics, publishing, and social contribution, all with with the aim to create an ideal world.">

<meta property="og:description" content="Official Website of HAPPY SCIENCE. HAPPY SCIENCE is a worldwide religious organization that spreads spiritual teachings to solve problems in life with love, enlightenment and faith. Our main teachings is the Fourfold Path which are “Love,” “Wisdom,” “Self-Reflection” and “Progress,” also called “The Principle of Happiness.” Members of HAPPY SCIENCE have faith in Lord El Cantare, the supreme God whose mission is to bring happiness to all humanity. The HAPPY SCIENCE GROUP is actively involved in many fields in addition to religion such as education, politics, publishing, and social contribution, all with with the aim to create an ideal world.">

<!-- ##### Who is Ryuho Okawa? ##### -->
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
<nav class="padding-bottom-md">
<h3 class="font-open-sans text-gold text-center padding-bottom-md"><strong class="font-600">Who is</strong> <br class="visible-sm">Ryuho Okawa?</h3>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8">
<p class="padding-bottom-md"><img class="img-responsive img-circle center-block" src="./HAPPY SCIENCE Official Website_files/kv-ryuho-okawa.png" alt="Ryuho Okawa"></p>
<!-- .col --></div>
<!-- .row --></div>

<p class="padding-bottom-sm padding-left-md padding-right-md" data-mh="tours-item" style="height: 120px;">Founder and CEO of Happy Science Group. Master Ryuho Okawa was born on July 7th, 1956 in Tokushima Prefecture, Japan.</p>
<p class="text-center padding-top-sm"><a class="btn btn-more" href="http://happy-science.org/ryuho-okawa/">LEARN MORE<span class="fa fa-angle-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>
</nav>
<!-- .col --></div>

<!-- ##### What is Happy Science? ##### -->
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
<nav class="padding-bottom-md">
<h3 class="font-open-sans text-gold text-center padding-bottom-md"><strong class="font-600">What is</strong> <br class="visible-sm">Happy Science?</h3>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8">
<p class="padding-bottom-md"><img class="img-responsive img-circle center-block" src="./HAPPY SCIENCE Official Website_files/kv-activities.png" alt="Happy Science"></p>
<!-- .col --></div>
<!-- .row --></div>

<p class="padding-bottom-sm padding-left-md padding-right-md" data-mh="tours-item" style="height: 120px;">Happy Science was founded on October 6th, 1986 and was certified in Japan as a religious organization on March 7th, 1991.</p>
<p class="text-center padding-top-sm"><a class="btn btn-more" href="http://happy-science.org/activities/">LEARN MORE<span class="fa fa-angle-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>
</nav>
<!-- .col --></div>

<!-- ##### How to join us? ##### -->
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
<nav class="padding-bottom-md">
<h3 class="font-open-sans text-gold text-center padding-bottom-md"><strong class="font-600">How to</strong> <br class="visible-sm">join us?</h3>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8">
<p class="padding-bottom-md"><img class="img-responsive img-circle center-block" src="./HAPPY SCIENCE Official Website_files/kv-joinus.png" alt="Join Us"></p>
<!-- .col --></div>
<!-- .row --></div>

<p class="padding-bottom-sm padding-left-md padding-right-md" data-mh="tours-item" style="height: 120px;">To join Happy Science is a precious moment in everyone’s life. A ceremony will be held in accordance to the type of membership you choose – a member or a devotee member.</p>

<h4><a class="text-gold" href="http://info.happy-science.org/2018/690/" title="HAPPY SCIENCE Monthly 289 is released!">HAPPY SCIENCE Monthly 289 is released!</a></h4>

</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-20d2d7d07ef691626788"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h1 class="text-align-center">Kashi Ashram is an interfaith spiritual community based on kindness, compassion and service, embracing the sacred practices of many traditions.&nbsp;</h1><p class="text-align-center">Kashi, meaning <em>‘City of Light’</em>, is one of the names for the ancient Indian city of Varanasi. However, Sebastian, Florida,&nbsp;has its own <em>‘City of Light’,&nbsp;</em>founded by <a href="https://www.kashi.org/ma-jaya">Ma Jaya Sati Bhagavati</a> in 1976.</p></div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-3 span-3" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_396"><div class="sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image sqs-text-ready" data-block-type="5" id="block-yui_3_17_2_23_1504460111116_95436"><div class="sqs-block-content" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_395">

	<time class="summary-metadata-item summary-metadata-item--date">Apr 24, 2018</time>
	

	











</div>
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary">

	

	











</div>
            </div>

            
              
            
            
            
              
              <!-- Excerpt -->
                <div class="summary-excerpt">
                  <p>This class is for EVERYBODY!&nbsp;<br>It allows you to work at your own level. All postures are optional, depending what you're able to do that day. You will increase flexibility and strength while reducing stress, tension and tightness. The class includes seated and standing poses utilizing a chair for support, but not getting down on the mat. It is great for beginners of any age or if recuperating from surgery or illness.</p>
                </div>

</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_49_1494699295412_22881"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h2 class="text-align-center"><a href="https://www.kashi.org/community">Intentional Community</a></h2><p>Kashi is a growing residential spiritual community. We are part of an international movement of intentional communities and ecovillages working towards cultivating spiritually, socially, and environmentally conscious lifestyles rooted in community.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="sqs-block spacer-block sqs-block-spacer sized vsize-1" data-block-type="21" id="block-yui_3_17_2_22_1498840755143_22278"><div class="sqs-block-content">&nbsp;</div></div><div class="row sqs-row" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_494"><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_493"><div class="sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image sqs-text-ready" data-aspect-ratio="54.880694143167034" data-block-type="5" id="block-yui_3_17_2_5_1496328530851_20911"><div class="sqs-block-content" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_492">

  

  	
      <div class="image-block-outer-wrapper layout-caption-hidden design-layout-inline" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_491">
      
        <div class="intrinsic" style="max-width:800.0px;" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_490">
          
            <a href="https://www.kashi.org/visit" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_489">
          
            <div style="padding-bottom: 54.8807%; overflow: hidden;" class="image-block-wrapper   has-aspect-ratio" data-description="" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_488">

            </a>
          

          

        </div>
      
      </div>
    

  


</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_5_1496328530851_20014"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h2 class="text-align-center"><a href="https://www.kashi.org/visit">visit / volunteer</a></h2><p>Are you on a spiritual path? Are you looking to make a difference in the world? Kashi offers many opportunities to visit, connect with like-minded people, and get involved.&nbsp;Choose from our Kashi Immersion Workstudy, hands on service, eco volunteer, or general volunteer positions. Work exchange positions are often open too.</p></div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_513"><div class="sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image sqs-text-ready" data-aspect-ratio="56.399132321041215" data-block-type="5" id="block-yui_3_17_2_5_1496328530851_18212"><div class="sqs-block-content" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_512">

            <a href="https://www.kashi.org/giving" id="yui_3_17_2_1_1524584695934_509">

</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_5_1496328530851_17342"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h2 class="text-align-center"><a href="https://www.kashi.org/giving">Giving</a></h2><p>In order for Kashi to thrive and have a larger impact on the world, the community needs resources and support – both financial and professional. Kashi's fundraising efforts are intended to strengthen and communicate Kashi’s message of radical acceptance and the sacred nature of all spiritual paths.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="sqs-block horizontalrule-block sqs-block-horizontalrule" data-block-type="47" id="block-yui_3_17_2_17_1498840755143_207850"><div class="sqs-block-content"><hr></div></div><div class="sqs-block quote-block sqs-block-quote null" data-block-type="31" id="block-yui_3_17_2_17_1494699295412_52481"><div class="sqs-block-content"><figure>
  <blockquote>
    <span>“</span>“The question for us now is, how can <br>we make a bigger impact?” <span>”</span>
  </blockquote>
  <figcaption class="source">— Swami Durga Das Hutner, CEO</figcaption>
</figure></div></div><div class="sqs-block horizontalrule-block sqs-block-horizontalrule" data-block-type="47" id="block-yui_3_17_2_15_1494703612825_13745"><div class="sqs-block-content"><hr></div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html sqs-col-5 span-5 float float-left" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_2_1498070642123_98497"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h1>Community News</h1></div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_7_1494702304529_34587"><div class="sqs-block-content"><p>Yoga, meditation, and community service are being recognized as integral aspects of a balanced life. Kashi has been involved in these practices for over 40 years.</p></div></div><div class="sqs-block summary-v2-block sqs-block-summary-v2" data-block-json="{&quot;hSize&quot;:null,&quot;floatDir&quot;:null,&quot;collectionId&quot;:&quot;590f95661b631b504827ab29&quot;,&quot;design&quot;:&quot;carousel&quot;,&quot;headerText&quot;:&quot;Featured&quot;,&quot;textSize&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;pageSize&quot;:10,&quot;imageAspectRatio&quot;:&quot;1.5&quot;,&quot;columnWidth&quot;:206,&quot;gutter&quot;:60,&quot;listImageSize&quot;:30,&quot;listImageAlignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;slidesPerRow&quot;:4,&quot;textAlignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;showTitle&quot;:true,&quot;showThumbnail&quot;:true,&quot;showExcerpt&quot;:true,&quot;showReadMoreLink&quot;:false,&quot;showPrice&quot;:true,&quot;productQuickViewEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;showPastOrUpcomingEvents&quot;:&quot;upcoming&quot;,&quot;metadataPosition&quot;:&quot;below-content&quot;,&quot;primaryMetadata&quot;:&quot;date&quot;,&quot;secondaryMetadata&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;filter&quot;:{&quot;featured&quot;:true,&quot;category&quot;:null},&quot;autoCrop&quot;:true,&quot;lightbox&quot;:false,&quot;mixedContent&quot;:true,&quot;blockId&quot;:&quot;e5ca96f802e93b65f6bb&quot;}" data-block-type="55" id="block-yui_3_17_2_17_1494699295412_11624"><div class="sqs-block-content">

                <a href="https://www.kashi.org/news/2017/6/21/now-accepting-wwoof-applications-for-sustainable-kashi-2017-2018" class="summary-title-link">Now Accepting WWOOF Applications for 2018</a></div>
            

            <!-- Metadata (Below Title) -->
            <div class="summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-title">
            
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary">

	
	<!-- Timestamp -->
	<time class="summary-metadata-item summary-metadata-item--date" datetime="2017-06-21">Jun 21, 2017</time>
	











</div>
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary">

	











</div>
            </div>

            
              
            
            
            
              
              <!-- Excerpt -->
                <div class="summary-excerpt">
                  <p>We are now accepting applications for the Sustainable Kashi 2018 WWOOF program! The program is hosted in our off-grid eco-village and is designed to teach and demonstrate how to reconnect with our precious eco-system.</p>
                </div>
              

              

              
            

            <!-- Metadata (Below Content) -->
            <div class="summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-content">

</div>
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary">

	











</div>
            </div>

              <!-- Title -->
              <div class="summary-title">
                <a href="https://www.kashi.org/news/2017/5/7/community-dinner-blog" class="summary-title-link">Kashi Ashram diversifying to ensure its survival</a></div>
            

            <!-- Metadata (Below Title) -->
            <div class="summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-title">
            
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary">

	
	<!-- Timestamp -->
	<time class="summary-metadata-item summary-metadata-item--date" datetime="2017-05-07">May 7, 2017</time>
	











</div>
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary">

	











</div>
            </div>

            
              
            
            
            
              
              <!-- Excerpt -->
                <div class="summary-excerpt">
                  <p>It’s been almost five years since Ma Jaya Sati Bhagavati, the spiritual head of Kashi Ashram, died and the community is undergoing a transformation to help secure its future.</p>
                </div>
              

              

              
            

            <!-- Metadata (Below Content) -->
            <div class="summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-content">
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary">

	
	<!-- Timestamp -->
	<time class="summary-metadata-item summary-metadata-item--date" datetime="2017-05-07">May 7, 2017</time>
	











</div>
              
              <div class="summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary">

	











</div>
            </div>

	<!-- MAM ANDELSKY SEN -->
	
	<table class="tbl_txt" align="center">
		<tbody><tr><td height="30"></td></tr>
		<tr><td height="30"><a name="mam_andelsky_sen"></a></td></tr>
		<tr>
			<td align="center">
				<span style="color: Red; line-height: 130%; font-size: 180%;"><b>I&nbsp; HAVE&nbsp; AN&nbsp; ANGELIC&nbsp; DREAM</b></span><br><br><br>
				<span style="color: Navy; line-height: 130%; font-size: 120%;">
					I have an angelic dream that one day earthly nations will rise up 
and live out the true meaning of their creed: 'We hold these truths to 
be self-evident, that all men are created equal.'<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that one day on the planet Earth, the sons 
of Angels of Heaven and the sons of former Angels of Darkness will be 
able to sit down together at the table of love and brotherhood.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that one day even the planet Earth, the 
desert planet, a planet sweltering with the heat of injustice, 
sweltering with the heat of slavery and oppression, will be transformed 
into an oasis of freedom and justice.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that My children of Earth will one day live
 on this planet where they will not be judged by their position and role
 but by the content of their character.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that people will begin speaking in CZECH  
in A SINGLE planetary language and will throw away 7000 different 
languages poked here by the infernal saurians from lots of other worlds 
so that people could never understand themselves.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that people on the Earth will begin using 
their SPIRITUAL HEARTS in their lives, where they have Creators highest
 truth, love, wisdom, good and intelligence and the avails from these.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that one day, people will begin using the 
technologies only for their USE, use of planet Earth and the entire 
Creation, and will stop slaving for useless things, and that they, once 
for all, get rid of all weapons given here by the saurians from hells.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that people will eliminate all infernal 
media that destroy peoples lives, manipulate them, misinform and 
confuse them and disallow them to attain happiness, health, love, truth,
 wisdom and all uses from these.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that one day, people will begin looking up 
to the East instead of the West, i.e., to the INCREASE OF LIGHT  the 
love and truth, thus to the path of THE ASCENSION TO THE HEAVENS.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that every day, people will sing together 
in joy, happiness and health and work for society a minimum of time much
 like the Angels in Heavens do. In 2009, this is 4 hours a day and, 
after due transformation of the infernal sucking system into the 
heavenly system, this would be just 2 hours a day.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that one day the puppet-mankind on the 
planet Earth shall rise up from the manacles of remote control by the 
Forces of Darkness, cease pointless slaving for material regarded as a 
god, and take its life into its own hands by means of THE PRIME 
CREATOR'S PURE LOVE.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that mankind will throw away the yoke of 
curse of the negative state, will cease once and for all being a 
puppet-mankind of the saurians from Darkness, and will join THE BIG 
HEAVENLY FAMILY OF ANGELIC WORLDS IN A PURE LOVE just as it has been 
since time immemorial  since times of creation by THE PRIME CREATOR OF 
ALL AND EVERYTHING !<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					I have an angelic dream that this mankind will fly up free to the 
Heavens, and it will keep its experience of the world of slavery and 
fallacy just for the reason of never again coming under seducement and 
temptation of the Forces of Darkness and their negative state.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					This angelic dream I see in beautiful bright colors as the future 
of people on the planet Earth which they choose in understanding that 
only PURE LOVE IN THEIR HEARTS SETS THEM FREE !<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					There is no force to stop this angelic dream, for THE LIGHT WINS 
AND THE LIGHT IS THE SOURCE OF LIFE given to us as a gift from THE PRIME
 CREATOR OF ALL AND EVERYTHING, WHO HAS BEEN FOR EONS EVERYWHERE AND IN 
EVERYTHING  THE ABSOLUTE LOVE, WISDOM, GOOD, TRUTH AND INTELLIGENCE.<br><font style="line-height: 75%;"><br></font>
					Given to all of you, dear people, by THE LORD JESUS CHRIST.<br><font style="line-height: 80%;"><br></font>
				</span>
			</td>

	<!-- MILUJTE SE A MEJTE SE RADI -->
	
	<table class="tbl_txt" align="center">
		<tbody><tr>
			<td colspan="3" align="center"><font style="color: Red; line-height: 130%; font-size: 180%;">LOVE EACH OTHER</font><br><br>
				<font style="color: Blue; line-height: 130%; font-size: 120%;">

	<!-- MIL A VEN -->
	
	<table class="tbl_txt" align="center">
		<tbody><tr>
			<td style="color: Blue; line-height: 130%; font-size: 120%;" align="center"><font style="color: Red; font-size: 150%;">"Dear people,</font><br><br>
				I am asking you to have just 1 minute of time and to read this text 
to the end. Try to visualize our beautiful blue planet Earth, nicely 
shining in the space. She is beautiful and living.<br><font style="line-height: 50%;"><br></font>
				She is giving us everything we need for living.<br><font style="line-height: 50%;"><br></font>
				Now she is in jeopardy - "thanks" to our behavior, she is in the danger of&nbsp;destruction.<br>
				She needs our help urgently. Within our hearts is hidden a true and 
real love - this is what our Mother Earth needs the most.<br>
				Therefore, let's send this love in a thought to our beautiful and 
graceful Earth - EVERY DAY at 9 p.m., for at least 10 minutes.<br><br>
				Because if she dies, we will die too&nbsp;!!!"<br>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr><td height="60"></td></tr>
	</tbody></table>

function zobraz_mesto()
{
	var idx = Math.round(Math.random() * (m.length-1));
	
	document.getElementById("id_evac_polozka_1").innerHTML = m[idx][0];
	document.getElementById("id_evac_polozka_2").innerHTML = m[idx][1];
	document.getElementById("id_evac_polozka_3").innerHTML = m[idx][2];
	document.getElementById("id_evac_polozka_4").innerHTML = m[idx][3];
	document.getElementById("id_evac_polozka_5").innerHTML = m[idx][4];
}

function prepni_mesto() 
{
	setTimeout('prepni_mesto()', 5000);
	zobraz_mesto();
}

napln_pole_mest();

<article id="post-222" class="post-222 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/06/26/sheeple-come-back-to-thee-fold/" rel="bookmark">Sheeple, come back to thee&nbsp;fold</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Blessed morning to all dearest menions of the Slavenation.</p>
<p>It has been awhile since an official sermon has been posted and for that, High Priestess Amanda and myself are dearly sorry. While we regularly host services for our US-based lemmings, we have sadly neglected our international readership. This shall not happen again. Ye shall not wait again for thine divine blessings!</p>
<p>We of the True Faith have a milestone announcement to make:</p>
<p><strong>High Priestess Amanda has recently purchased our first Join Our Concubine Church van!!!</strong></p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="239" data-permalink="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/06/26/sheeple-come-back-to-thee-fold/2016-06-18-1/" data-orig-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg?w=1108" data-orig-size="600,450" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="2016-06-18 (1)" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg?w=1108?w=300" data-large-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg?w=1108?w=600" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-239" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/2016-06-18-1.jpg" alt="2016-06-18 (1)" srcset="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg 600w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg?w=150 150w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/2016-06-18-1.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"></p>
<p>Isn’t she breathtaking? The glorious turquoise color reminds me of the shimmering serenity of the sea…which matches the all-encompassing omnipotence of your leaders.</p>
<p>This van runs on love and gasoline, but remember, nothing in life is free (except your servitude and labor duh). We implore you to continue tithing like the true followers that you are! Only those who give of their material possessions will be allowed to ride with us with us on our journey to the Ninth Gate of Eternal Bliss.</p>
<p><strong>Send all your worldly assets and life savings to us now for a front seat ticket on the glory van to eternal life and slaveation!&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>Namaste,</p>
<p>High Priestess Daneka + Amanda</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

<article id="post-183" class="post-183 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/03/02/birthday-blessings-to-the-high-priestess/" rel="bookmark">Birthday Blessings to the High&nbsp;Priestess</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Menions of the true faith:</p>
<p>A very important annual event is on the threshold and your attendance is not only expected, but required. We of Join Our Concubine are proud to present…</p>
<p>First Annual Piscean High Priestess Birthday Ceremony</p>
<p>You are cordially invited to partake in the eating of Fudgie the Whale cake, washed down with our sacred drink Tang (or beer for the buffoons amongst us), and dance the night away around a fire pit singing psalms of praise and worship. A special live sermon will be delivered by your High Priestesses that you will not want to miss. Or shall we say, YE SHALL NOT DARE TO MISS.</p>
<p>Please arrive in cult attire aka white, or at minimum, light colors. It matters not that it is before Labor Day, WE COMMAND THEE. I expect every loyal menion to be in attendance as my original concept of a clown-themed extravaganza was met with much dismay by the larger family. As your omnipotent leader, I try my best to consider the opinion of others and ultimately, I wanted you little pissants to have a great evening. I mostly certainly did not want anyone taking refuge in the McDonald’s across the street to escape childhood fears. Though I will point out that Ronald resides in the land of the golden arches and I did consider briefly hiring the folks at McD’s for an official birthday kickoff complete with Happy Meals because I’m basically a 5 year old. Anyway I digress….</p>
<p>Saturday March 12. 9pm. Hot Bird. Wear white. Bow to me upon entrance. Come bearing gifts of Frankincense and Myrr. Drink sweet beverages and partake in free love with thy fellow lemmings.</p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="217" data-permalink="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/03/02/birthday-blessings-to-the-high-priestess/source-family-2/" data-orig-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg?w=1108" data-orig-size="640,455" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="source family" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg?w=1108?w=300" data-large-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg?w=1108?w=640" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-217" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/source-family.jpg" alt="source family" srcset="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg 640w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg?w=150 150w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/03/source-family.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"></p>

<article id="post-175" class="post-175 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/02/04/we-command-thee/" rel="bookmark">We command thee…</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><img data-attachment-id="176" data-permalink="https://joinourconcubine.com/2016/02/04/we-command-thee/command-thee/" data-orig-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=1108" data-orig-size="1024,768" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="command thee" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=1108?w=300" data-large-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=1108?w=1024" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-176" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/command-thee.jpg" alt="command thee" srcset="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg 1024w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=150 150w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=300 300w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/command-thee.jpg?w=768 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></p>
<p>Sermon to come Saturday. Stay tuned loyal lemmings…</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">

<article id="post-109" class="post-109 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/12/27/merry-cultsmas-from-our-family-to-yours/" rel="bookmark">Merry Cultsmas from our Family to&nbsp;yours</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Good morning dear menions on this fresh post-holiday morning! We hope that all our devotees had an amazing December full of holiday cheer and are amped up for the upcoming New Year! A couple weeks ago, Amanda and I hosted our annual High Priestess Summit where we began our preparations and plotted our vision for 2016. It was simply a riveting success!</p>
<p><em>Amanda sharing her worldly assets for all beloved concubines</em></p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="119" data-permalink="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/12/27/merry-cultsmas-from-our-family-to-yours/img_4584/" data-orig-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg?w=1108" data-orig-size="480,640" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone 6s&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1449955219&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.15&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.066666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_4584" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg?w=1108?w=225" data-large-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg?w=1108?w=480" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-119" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/img_4584.jpg" alt="IMG_4584" srcset="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg 480w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg?w=113 113w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_4584.jpg?w=225 225w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px"></p>
<p><em>Our spirits filled with the divine inspiration of Paul Reubens, we celebrated the success of the 2015 Summit with holiday cookies and Mexican culinary delights</em></p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="124" data-permalink="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/12/27/merry-cultsmas-from-our-family-to-yours/img_4585/" data-orig-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg?w=1108" data-orig-size="640,480" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone 6s&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1449955304&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.15&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;500&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.066666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_4585" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg?w=1108?w=300" data-large-file="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg?w=1108?w=640" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/img_45851.jpg" alt="IMG_4585" srcset="https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg 640w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg?w=150 150w, https://joinmyconcubine.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/img_45851.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"></p>
<p>Before we launch into what can be expected of the Family in the New Year, let’s recap the milestones of Join Our Concubine to date.</p>
<p>Firstly, we are now a global powerhouse! With pious menions on every continent, spreading the word far and wide, our numbers are vast and growing by the day. In fact, our devoted Australian brother Krissan has been hard at work in the land down under to locate a spirit animal for our worship: a majestic kangeroo. The kangeroo is the perfect totem for our Family in that while the kangeroo is often illustrated in popular culture as a friendly but ludicrous creature, those mofos will not hesitate to claw out the eyes of one’s enemy. Take note, ye naysayers, ye nonbelievers of the True Word.<strong> Shun the non-believers!</strong></p>
<p>This year also saw the birth of our very first Psalm of Praise. Lifting our voices in worship is one of the most effective ways for a menion to show their devotion (besides the steady giving of tithes to the Family, obviously) and we welcome all voices that are capable of staying on key to sing and record their reverence to the true word. <strong>Open your mouths, open your hearts.</strong></p>
<p><em>High Priestess Amanda performs a lyrical masterpiece on the importance of faith</em></p>
<div class="embed-soundcloud"><iframe width="1108" height="400" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src="./Would you like to join our concubine_ – Free Love_ Inquire Within_files/saved_resource.html"></iframe></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>As you can see, we have so much to be proud of this year, but 2016 promises to be even more fruitful! We are currently working on designs so that we can start manufacturing official <strong>Join Our Concubine</strong> apparel! We find that one of the best marketing tools for our mission is simply to get people talking. What better way to alert the masses than a t-shirt or snapback hat that simply reads “I am a mindless lemming concubine.” Only the most virtuous of our followers will be chosen to be apparel ambassadors upon the initial clothing line debut, so ya’ll better make sure your tithing game is on point!</p>
<p><strong>High Priestess Amanda</strong> is currently visiting the notorious Sin City aka Las Vegas to climb some rocks, but most importantly to <strong>SAVE SOULS</strong>. Our west coast membership drive is in full swing and there are plenty of souls for the taking! We urge all menions to minister to everyone you meet because missionary efforts are the cornerstone of reaching the coveted <strong>Ninth Gate of Eternal Bliss</strong>.</p>
<p>On that note dear concubines, we bid thee farewell to 2015 and look forward to another round of spiritual awakenings in 2016. L Ron Hubbard’s space cadets got nothing on our ish! We are strong. We are united. We are <strong>ONE LOVE</strong>. <em>Voices raised, heads high, arms to the sky, Hail to the omnipotent Goddesses of the Divine, we tip our glasses and drinketh the blood of the mighty kangeroo in lascivious thirst!&nbsp;</em></p>
<p>Namaste,</p>
<p><strong>Daneka and Amanda, High Priestesses of the First Order.&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">

<article id="post-54" class="post-54 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/11/26/giving-thanks-the-join-our-concubine-way/" rel="bookmark">Giving Thanks the Join Our Concubine&nbsp;Way</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Good evening dear menions, on this crisp Thanksgiving Day Eve. Many of our most loyal followers live overseas on this glorious American holiday (shoutout to the pious <strong>Brother Gary</strong> in Dubai, who relentlessly spreads the good word to all the lost heretics in the Middle East!) and so cannot be here to celebrate with the family, but we send them all our omnipotent best wishes from afar.</p>
<p>This holiday is about family, love, and giving selflessly to others. Instead of watching the plebian sport of football and pigging out on feasts of the avian persuasion (that may or may not have bird flu), we hope that all menions will consider how they can best give selflessly to the church. There are many ways to contribute to the mission of the family, but the most valuable ways to be of service are to give of one’s time and worldly assets.</p>
<p>We urge everyone in the <strong>Join Our Concubine</strong> community to spend some time tomorrow spreading the mission of the family to all of those heathens who may be within our midst. Can ye dareth to believe that there are lost souls out there for the taking? It is true, dear menions, and it is sad.&nbsp;With the year ending upon us, and a new year to come, we must remember that life is fleeting. We simply cannot afford to let these wandering sheep walk straight into the slaughterhouse. <strong>WE ARE THE TEMPLE.</strong> The truth. The guiding light. It is imperative that we show them the way.</p>
<p>It is also incredibly important that the church continues to operate at its highest and unfortunately, it is simply not possible without the monetary donations of its members. Those Taco Tuesdays events don’t pay for themselves! Last Amanda and I checked (which was this morning), we have been unable to conjure tacos to rain from the skies but do not fret, your tireless leaders practice our taco manifestations daily! Until then, we need all of you to be diligent in the giving of your tithes and offerings to the family.</p>
<p>It is proclaimed in the Bible that one must give 10% of one’s earnings. The church of <strong>Join Our Concubine</strong> cannot continue to save souls with your mere 10% crumbs. No, alas, we need your <strong>BREAD</strong>. And tortillas as well, as those are <strong>bread</strong> too. <strong>High Priestess Amanda</strong> has been called upon to the great city of Chicago this December for a leadership convention and she must arrive in the finest transportation. A cult leader of her stature simply cannot abide driving up in a Ford.</p>
<p>Giving thanks. Giving love. Giving monetary assets of value. Blessings from on high! The omnipotent leaders <strong>Amanda</strong> and <strong>Daneka</strong> wish all of you a magnificent and joyous holiday.</p>
<p>Namaste,</p>
<p><strong>Daneka and Amanda – High Priestesses of the 1st Order.&nbsp;</strong></p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<ul class="post-meta"><li class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://joinourconcubine.com/author/koolikowska/">koolikowska</a></li><li class="posted-on"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/11/26/giving-thanks-the-join-our-concubine-way/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-11-26T01:08:08+00:00">November 26, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2015-11-26T02:00:01+00:00">November 26, 2015</time></a></li></ul><!-- .post-metadata -->			<div class="meta-wrapper">

<article id="post-37" class="post-37 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
		
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://joinourconcubine.com/2015/10/29/cult-updates/" rel="bookmark">Cult Updates!</a></h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p style="text-align:left;">Good evening, dear patient sheeplings! I know that you are all waiting patiently on the edge of your seats for our next sermon, and do not fret, as it is coming and will be well worth the wait. The truth awaits all those who dareth to read!</p>
<p>Tonight though, I come bearing riveting news. Hold on to your seats! I am <strong><em>very</em></strong>&nbsp;excited to announce that our cult is making great strides! We currently have devoted menions all over our great nation, as well as Canada, Brazil, France, Poland, UAE, South Africa, Japan, Singapore, and as of today, Brunei! The family is stronger than ever, and our numbers swell by the day! Ya’ll know I’m checking the analytics on this ‘ish. Your leadership never sleeps.</p>
<p>That’s right. We are <strong>GLOBAL</strong>. We are a <strong>family</strong>. We are <strong>one love</strong>. Please continue to spread the word (and your legs dear menions) far and wide, because we are coming for <em>you,</em> future concubines and your <em>ass</em>ets!</p>
<div class="_209g _2vxa"></div>
<div class="_209g _2vxa">With love, ame, amour, miłość,&nbsp;الحب, lief,&nbsp;愛,&nbsp;爱, &amp; suka,</div>
<div class="_209g _2vxa"><strong>– Daneka</strong> and <strong>Amanda</strong>, High Priestesses of the 1st order</div>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">

			if (typeof Gravatar === "undefined"){

			}			

			Gravatar.profile_cb = function( hash, id ) {
				WPGroHo.syncProfileData( hash, id );
			};
			Gravatar.my_hash = WPGroHo.my_hash;
			Gravatar.init( 'body', '#wp-admin-bar-my-account' );
		});
	</script>

	<div id="left-col">
		<h2>About Us</h2>
<div id="who">
<p><strong>Who We Are | </strong>The Family International (TFI) is an online Christian network of individuals in over 80 countries, committed to sharing the message of God’s love with others. <a href="https://www.thefamilyinternational.org/en/about/">Learn more about us</a></p>
</div>
<div id="what">
<p><strong>What We Do | </strong>Members strive to share a message of faith and hope for all nations and to make a difference in their local community. <a href="https://www.thefamilyinternational.org/en/mission-statement/">Read our mission statement</a></p>
</div>
<div id="why">
<p><strong>Why We Do It | </strong>Love is God's solution to the problems the world faces, even in the complex and challenging world we live in today. Love put into action is the greatest service to humankind. <a href="http://www.thefamily.org/">Visit our community site</a></p>
</div>
	</div>

                <article id="content" class="row">


                    
                    <main itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" class="main col-12">
                    

                    

                    
    

<div class="row justify-content-center">
	<div class="home-sidebar home-sidebar--left">
		<div class="blocked-hover--bg sidebar__item sidebar__item mt-0 mb-0">
	<a href="http://www.lronhubbard.org/biography.html" class="no-decoration d-block">
    	<h6 class="subheader--title">
	        
	            L. RON HUBBARD: A&nbsp;PROFILE
	        
	    </h6>
	</a>

    <a href="http://www.lronhubbard.org/ron-series/profile/introduction.html">
        <img class=" lazyloaded" data-src="https://files.ondemandhosting.info/imagecache/scalefit-250x300@as=1/data/www.scientology.org/themes/www_scientology_org2/images/ron-series-profile_en_US.jpg" src="./Official Church of Scientology_ What is Scientology__files/ron-series-profile_en_US.jpg">
    </a>

    <div class="right-side">

        <div class="sidebar__item--body-copy">
            This all-encompassing compendium for <em>The L.&nbsp;Ron Hubbard Series</em> highlights all he achieved as a humanitarian, educator, administrator, philosopher and artist. It further presents the only complete chronological overview of his life and discoveries.
        </div>

        <a href="http://www.lronhubbard.org/ron-series/profile/introduction.html" class="main-button sidebar-button">
            
<div class="button--more-info draw-border ">
	<div class="button--external-link">
	</div>
	<span>VIEW ONLINE</span> 
	
	
<svg class="" version="1.1" id="Layer_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 8 12" style="enable-background:new 0 0 8 12;" xml:space="preserve">
<g id="Artboard" transform="translate(-707.000000, -1725.000000)">
	<polygon id="keyboard_arrow_right---material-copy-2" points="707.9,1735.3 712.1,1731.1 707.9,1726.9 709.2,1725.6 714.7,1731.1 
		709.2,1736.6 	"></polygon>
</g>
</svg>

	
</div>

        </a>
    </div>

</div>


		<div class="mt-2">
			<div class="sidebar__faq">
    <h6 class="subheader--title">
		MOST ASKED QUESTIONS
	</h6>
    <ul class="faq-block-listing">

        <li><a class="listing-item" href="https://www.scientology.org/what-is-scientology/the-practice-of-scientology.html">What are the Fundamental <br> Practices of the Religion?</a></li>
        <li><a class="listing-item" href="https://www.scientology.org/faq/scientology-and-dianetics-auditing/what-is-auditing.html">What is Auditing?</a></li>

				</h5>

OCTOBER 18, 2015

	

					</div>

SAINT HILL, EAST GRINSTEAD, UNITED KINGDOM

					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="main__news-listing-blurb">
					
Saint Hill in East Grinstead, UK carries monumental significance in Scientology. It’s where Scientology Founder L.&nbsp;Ron&nbsp;Hubbard lived, researched and accomplished revolutionary discoveries on the spirit and life, and ensured the religion’s dynamic future. And with its dedication as Ideal, Mr. Hubbard’s vision is fully realized in the majesty that is the Ideal Saint Hill.

<a class="blocked-hover no-decoration" href="http://www.lronhubbard.org/">
	<div class="blocked-hover--bg ml-0">
		<h2 class="block-hover__title">
			L. RON HUBBARD<br>
			<span class="not-bold">Founder of Dianetics &amp; Scientology</span>
		</h2>
		<p>There are only two tests of a life well lived, L. Ron Hubbard once remarked: Did one do as one intended? And were people glad one lived? In testament to the first stands the full body of his life’s work, including the more than 12,000 writings and 3,000 tape-recorded lectures of Dianetics and Scientology.
</p>
		<div class="learn-more-link with-underline">
			LEARN MORE
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
	</div>
</a>

<div class="clearfix"></div>

<a class="blocked-hover no-decoration" href="https://www.scientology.org/what-is-scientology.html">
	<div class="blocked-hover--bg">
		<h2 class="block-hover__title">
			WHAT IS SCIENTOLOGY?

		</h2>
		<p>Scientology is a religion in its highest meaning, as it helps bring Man to total freedom and truth. The essential tenets of Scientology are these:
</p>
		<div class="pl-2">
			<p></p><p>You are an immortal spiritual being.</p>
<p>Your experience extends well beyond a single lifetime. And your capabilities are unlimited, even if not presently realized.</p>
<p>Furthermore, Man is basically good. He is seeking to survive. And his survival depends upon himself and his fellows and his attainment of brotherhood with the universe.</p>
<p></p>
		</div>
		<div class="learn-more-link with-underline">
			LEARN MORE
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
	</div>
</a>

<div class="clearfix"></div>



<a class="blocked-hover no-decoration mb-0" href="https://www.scientology.org/david-miscavige/">
	<div class="blocked-hover--bg">
		<h2 class="block-hover__title">
			DAVID MISCAVIGE:<br>
			<span class="not-bold">At the Helm of Scientology’s Explosive Growth
</span>
		</h2>

		<p>David Miscavige is the ecclesiastical leader of the Scientology religion. From his position as Chairman of the Board Religious Technology Center (RTC), Mr. Miscavige bears the ultimate responsibility for ensuring the standard and pure application of L.&nbsp;Ron Hubbard’s technologies and Keeping Scientology Working.
</p>

		<div class="learn-more-link with-underline">
			LEARN MORE
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
	</div>
</a>

</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p><p><font color="FFFFFF"><font color="FF0000"><font color="ffffff"><font size="5"><font size="4"><font color="c0c0c0"><font color="00cc66"><font size="5"><font color="ff0000"><font size="4"><font color="FF0000"><font face="ARIAL">Spiritual Satanism strongly advocates all learning, knowledge, inquiry, and free thought. 

</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p><p><font color="FFFFFF"><font color="FF0000"><font color="ffffff"><font size="5"><font size="4"><font color="c0c0c0"><font color="00cc66"><font size="5"><font color="ff0000"><font size="4"><font color="FF0000"><font face="ARIAL">Spiritual Satanism supports the separation of church and state. Spiritual Satanists are free to live their lives as they choose- responsibility to the responsible. We live by natural law and encourage everyone to develop themselves to their fullest extent.

    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-8"><div class="ccm-custom-style-headerimagefull47">


        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-headerimagefull47-11553">
    <h5><em>At Desteni we thoroughly research and investigate the essence of what it means to live responsibly and fully. This research is done through the participation of everyone that is interested and dares to take on the journey of self-discovery. We share our findings through video, audio and text through various internet media. This website gathers all the relevant information and links you'll want to explore if you're interested in learning about Desteni.<br>
Enjoy!</em></h5>

    <div class="ccm-layout-column-wrapper" id="ccm-layout-column-wrapper-34"><div class="ccm-layout-column" id="ccm-layout-column-84"><div class="ccm-layout-column-inner"><div class="ccm-custom-style-main371">


    <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="text-align: center;">Explore</h1>

<h1 style="text-align: center;">the Desteni Material</h1>

</div></div></div></div>

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main3-11626">

    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main372-11627">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/abfff6c552d67415b17537d7c55a05af.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="100" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11627">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p class="MsoNormal">EQAFE is our online shop. Here you can find tons of products covering just about every topic you can think of. For self-directed learning with relevant and up-to-date information, EQAFE is your resource of choice.<o:p></o:p></p>

</div><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main374-11628">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/95e7cf31eafc314eab7238678a942d56.png" alt="" width="100" height="57" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11628">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p class="MsoNormal">Desteni 'I' Process offers both courses and coaching. The Free DIP Lite course is for many the ideal way to become acquainted with the Desteni material and tools.<o:p></o:p></p>

</div></div>
    </div>

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main3-11631">

    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main376-11632">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/7db1ec44c5a8f263168f9868eedae937.png" alt="" width="100" height="37" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11632">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p class="MsoNormal">Self &amp; Living is a series of videos with a focus on practical lifestyle creation, sharing simple yet effective solutions to common every-day-life issues and obstacles.<o:p></o:p></p>

</div><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main378-11634">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/0210eda4e855cc72cd48646f06773990.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="95" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11634">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p class="MsoNormal">The S.O.U.L. material revolves around the role and power of words in our lives and provides the step-by-step support and know-how to live words as expressions of ourselves on our journey of self-creation.<o:p></o:p></p>

</div></div>
    </div>

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main3-11636">

    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main380-11637">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/8f38d49fc62de6c24421d8d74b806bf8.png" alt="" width="97" height="100" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11637">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p class="MsoNormal">The Destonian Wiki initiative was started to gather all the relevant posts from the original Desteni Forums and making them more easily available. The Destonian Wiki is currently offline for maintenance.<span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;font-style:normal;mso-bidi-font-style:italic"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div><div class="columns medium-1">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main382-11639">
    <img src="./Desteni Homepage_files/a8ca3ebc36c1b4c8b6903db696be521c.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="79" class="ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-11639">
    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-5">

    <p>Hundreds of articles were written and released in the period from 2007-2010. When consulting the articles, hear the message/principles within them, yet always read them within the context of the time in which they were published – much has changed since.<o:p></o:p></p>

</div></div>
    </div>


    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-12">

    <div class=" text-center">
	<a href="http://desteni.org/desteni-material" class="button radius" target="">
		Learn More about What's What	</a>
</div>

</div></div>

    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-12">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main48587-11645">
    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Destonians Share</h2>

    </div>
</div></div>


    <div class="row"><div class="columns medium-6">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main48588-12190">
    <h6><em>"When in January this year the word Defeat came up in various series of the Eqafe recordings: What went down in me? – The word itself in my mind seemed to throw ahead a daunting shadow, and with a sinking feeling in me – I recognized that signature of something I’d accepted long ago as part of me, it carried with it a solemnity, like news of death, of something irreversible – and I did not want to listen to the interviews."</em></h6>

<h6 class="entry-title"><a href="https://adamsjourneyintolife.wordpress.com/2018/04/03/day-432-redefining-the-word-live-5/" target="_blank">Day 432: Redefining the word Live (5)</a></h6>

    </div>


        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main48588-12191">
    	<div id="youtube12191" class="youtubeBlock youtubeBlockResponsive16by9">
		<iframe class="youtube-player" src="./Desteni Homepage_files/NrPQZrUHRXw.html" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
	</div>

    </div>
</div><div class="columns medium-6">

        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main48589-12192">
    	<div id="youtube12192" class="youtubeBlock youtubeBlockResponsive16by9">
		<iframe class="youtube-player" src="./Desteni Homepage_files/0k0crZ1P-iU.html" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
	</div>

    </div>


        <div class="ccm-custom-style-container ccm-custom-style-main48589-12189">
    <h6 style="text-align: right;"><em>"Ever since I can remember, I have always felt that there was something that was not quite right about my reality. It didn’t matter where I went or what I did, there would always be something untouchable or unspeakable even though it often felt as though an explanation was just at the tip of my tongue. In search of answers, I’ve looked to the animals, nature and the faces of people, searched in my dreams, investigated the astral plane or what I thought was the astral plane and made it a point often to embrace as many demons as I could."</em></h6>

<h6 style="text-align: right;"><a href="http://thomaslagrua.blogspot.co.za/2018/04/strange-reality.html" target="_blank">Strange Reality</a></h6>

    </div>
</div></div>

<div id="main-content">


			
				<article id="post-855" class="post-855 page type-page status-publish hentry">

				
					<div class="entry-content">
					<div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_0 et_pb_fullwidth_section et_section_regular">
				
				
				
				
					<section class="et_pb_fullwidth_header et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_fullwidth_header_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_fullwidth_header_container left">
					<div class="header-content-container center">
					<div class="header-content">
						
						<h1 class="et_pb_module_header">The Apostles of Infinite Love</h1>
						<span class="et_pb_fullwidth_header_subhead">of the Order of the Magnificat of the Mother of God</span>
						<div class="et_pb_header_content_wrapper"> </div>
						
					</div>
				</div>
					
				</div>
				<div class="et_pb_fullwidth_header_overlay"></div>
				<div class="et_pb_fullwidth_header_scroll"></div>
			</section><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_fullwidth_image et-waypoint et_animated et_pb_fullwidth_image_0 fade et-animated" style="animation-duration: 500ms; animation-delay: 0ms; opacity: 0; animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;">
				
				
				<img src="./The Apostles of Infinite Love _ Monastery of the Apostles_files/pano_internet-1.jpg" alt="">
			
			</div>
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_1 et_section_regular">
				
				
				
				
					<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_0 et_pb_row_3-4_1-4">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_3_4  et_pb_column_0 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h1><em>The Apostles of Infinite Love</em></h1>
<p>The Order of the Magnificat of the Mother of God, established in the Province of Quebec since 1962, is also known by the name: The Apostles of Infinite Love. They were legally recognized as of 1963. Since 1973, they possess a federal charter for all of Canada, and one for the Province of Quebec by virtue of the Religious Corporations Act. The Apostles of Infinite Love are also recognized in Canada as a registered charity. Here in Canada, we labor mainly in Quebec, Ontario and British Columbia.</p>
<p>Our Religious Order also possesses charters in the United States, Puerto Rico, Guatemala, the Dominican Republic and Ecuador. It is recognized in Guadeloupe and in France, and established in Italy and in South Africa.</p>
<p>The Mother House and headquarters are situated at 290 7e Rang, Mont-Tremblant, Quebec J8E 1Y1. The chapel is open to the public and visitors often join us in prayer, especially on Sundays, during the periods of liturgical feasts such as Christmas, Holy Week and Easter, and during the Marian feast days of the Assumption and the Nativity of Mary. Each year, either singly or in small groups, retreatants come to stay on the Monastery grounds over a longer or shorter period of time, in individual little houses destined for visitors.</p>
<p>Besides adoration of the Most Blessed Sacrament, prayer, study and work of all kinds, the Community lends itself to all the spiritual and corporal works of mercy. Its main objectives are the preservation and teaching of the Christian Faith and charitable works of all kinds: assistance to the poor, teaching to children and adults, care of the sick and the elderly, aid to families, etc.</p>
<p>Here in the province of Quebec, among other houses, we have the House of Bread located in Quebec City, where since 1976, our Sisters provide hundreds of destitute people and families every day with food and care. At the Mother House in Mont-Tremblant and other nearby houses, very substantial food baskets are distributed each week to many families; we are often able to give clothing and shoes, and toys for children. These works are made possible thanks to the donations of benefactors who know and support our charitable activities.</p>
<p>Religious teaching is given in our places of worship and through various programs of instruction: sermons, conferences, courses, retreats and spiritual direction. It is also given largely and especially through the distribution of our books and magazines, prepared and printed at the Mother House of the Community.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->

<p><em>“We are gathered together here to be united to Jesus our Saviour, our Redeemer, who died for us on the cross to save souls. &nbsp;He is the Good Shepherd who wants to associate us to His work of salvation continued throughout the ages.” &nbsp;</em>(Father John Gregory)</p>

					<p>“Our Lord said to us in the Gospel, Go and teach all nations. &nbsp;He did not tell us to go and convince, but to teach, to convey His message, to sow the good seed. &nbsp;Men can accept the Divine Word or not; that is their concern. &nbsp;God makes the good seed grow in well-prepared hearts.” &nbsp; (Father John&nbsp;Gregory)</p>

<section class="dexp-section" id="section-clients">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<!-- .region-testimonial-->
  <div class="region region-testimonial col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
    <div id="block-views-testimonials-block-1" class="block block-views dexp-animate" data-animate="fadeInUpBig">
  
     
              <h3 class="block-title">Testimonies</h3>
           
         
<div class="content">
<div class="view view-testimonials view-id-testimonials view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-9914d7c491c0898781486b1e69a9cd5f">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div>
      
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <h3 class="field-content"><a href="https://twelvetribes.org/articles/redeemer">Redeemer</a></h3>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8"><p><em>"...help..."</em><br>
My desperate cry for help began as a whisper, slipping spontaneously from my lips. Late at night, alone in my darkened house, I couldn't sleep, I had paced miles of circles my house. I was hopelessly thinking in circles, too. Over and over I reconsidered what I had said; what she had said. What I did; what she did. What I would do next... or not.<br>
I had been anxiously, compulsively recollecting the same miserable scenario for weeks, months, many months. I was trapped, and there was no way out. I was lonely, and I hated that my phone rarely rang. But I dreaded it every time it did; it seemed like the only news I got was bad news.<br></p>
<br><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://twelvetribes.org/articles/redeemer" role="button">Read the Whole Story</a>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><img typeof="foaf:Image" alt="" src="./The Twelve Tribes _ We are the commonwealth of Israel... we have a wonderful story to tell_files/ayil-benyamin-of-yoceph.jpg" width="220" height="147"><p>(Ayil Benyamin)<br><i>Valley Center, CA</i></p></div>
</div>  </div>  </div>
    </div>

<!--#section-delivery-->
<section class="dexp-section" id="section-delivery">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<!-- .region-delivery-second-->
  <div class="region region-delivery-second col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
    <div id="block-views-front-nearest-community-block-2" class="block block-views">
  
     
              <h3 class="block-title">Nearest Community</h3>
           
         
<div class="content">
<div class="view view-front-nearest-community view-id-front_nearest_community view-display-id-block_2 view-dom-id-7c40ab99a3b7572efa635f9c5824ec3f">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
      
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="https://twelvetribes.org/community/coxsackie">Community in Coxsackie</a></span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>In 1998, one of our sisters drove down the hill looking for a laundromat. Instead, she found the quaint lower village of Coxsackie and its centerpiece, a three-story brick opera house from the late 1800s.&nbsp;This building, called the <em>Dolan Block,</em> would be center of a new community of believers. Over the next decade, we fixed up many of the buildings in town and started businesses, like the <em>Maté Factor</em> tea house and the<em> Simon the Tanner</em> shoes and clothing store. A fire came in 2003, and many of the local people came to help us afterwards, and we were so thankful for the friends we had made. In 2009, we made a mistake, closed down our community and sending everyone to&nbsp;other communities, and almost sold the buildings.</p></div>  </div>  </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
      <div class="view-footer">
      <p><a href="https://twelvetribes.org/community/coxsackie" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Visit This Community</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://twelvetribes.org/locations" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">List All Communities</a></p>
    </div>
  
  
</div>
</div>
</div>  </div>
<!-- END .region-delivery-second-->

  <div class="region region-bottom-first col-xs-12 col-sm-3 col-md-3 col-lg-3">
    <div id="block-block-4" class="block block-block dexp-animate" data-animate="fadeInLeft">
<div class="content">
<p><img src="./The Twelve Tribes _ We are the commonwealth of Israel... we have a wonderful story to tell_files/logo-en-rev.png"></p>
<p>The Twelve Tribes is a confederation of twelve self-governing tribes, composed of self-governing communities. We are disciples of the Son of God whose name in Hebrew is Yahshua. We follow the pattern of the early church in Acts 2:44 and 4:32, truly believing everything that is written in the Old and New Covenants of the Bible, and sharing all things in common.</p>



</div>
</div>  </div>
<!-- END .region-bottom-first-->

			<div id="content2" role="main">


                <div class="contentuant">
		<div class="leftist"> <span class="the-hometitle">welcome</span>
			
			<p>Jesus People USA (JPUSA for short) is both a church AND a community. For what is church, but people, the body of Christ. Definitely the lines which usually separate our Sunday self from who we are the other six days of the week get blurred. It is a place to discover who you are and to be challenged to live an authentic life in Christ.</p>
<p><a title="ABOUT US" href="http://jpusa.org/about-us/">Read More.</a></p>
			
             </div> <!--.leftist -->
             <div class="righty">

<div style="width:230px; height: 167px; background-color:#999; color: #fff; text-align:center; padding-top:40px; font-size:32px; line-height:40px; float:left; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold;">
<h2>Join Us<br>For<br><a href="http://jpusa.org/church/">Worship</a></h2>
</div>
